    <CMUI_Label name="lblInstructions" id="38601829-460a-4d21-ad04-05d667105639">
        <alignment>1</alignment>
        <caption>NOTE: This process should not be run while other developers are working!

Enter the name of a local file directory (or click the browse button to look for one), generated schemas will be written to this directory.  Then click "Start" to begin.

Once completed, check the JMT System Alerts for any warnings/conflicts.  When satisfied, load the schemas back into the development environment, then reload the translation Global Constants using the "Reload" button on JMT's Text Translation screen.</caption>
